\begin_layout Standard
根式函数式幂函数的反函数，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
w=\sqrt[n]{z}\iff w^{n}=z,\quad w,z\in\mathbb{C}
\]

\end_inset

设
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
z=\rho\ee^{\ii\theta},\quad\theta\in[0,2\pi),\rho\in(0,\infty)
\]

\end_inset

则 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt[n]{z}$
\end_inset

