\begin_layout Standard
亚纯函数 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)$
\end_inset

 在其零点或极点 
\begin_inset Formula $z=s$
\end_inset

 附近总是可以表示为 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)=(z-s)^{k}g(z)$
\end_inset

，其中 
\begin_inset Formula $k\in\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $g(z)$
\end_inset

 在 
\begin_inset Formula $z=s$
\end_inset

 附近解析且 
\begin_inset Formula $g(s)\ne0$
\end_inset

。由等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{f'(z)}{f(z)}=\frac{\left[(z-s)^{k}\right]'g(z)+(z-s)^{k}g'(z)}{(z-s)^{k}g(z)}=\frac{k}{z-s}+\frac{g'(z)}{g(z)}
\]

\end_inset

可知：
\begin_inset Formula $z=s$
\end_inset

 是 
\begin_inset Formula $f'(z)/f(z)$
\end_inset

 的一阶极点。设 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 为不经过 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)$
\end_inset

 的零点或极点的任意简单闭合路径，由
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "thm:留数定理"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2\pi\ii}\oint_{C}\frac{f'(z)}{f(z)}\dd{z}=\sum_{s\in C}k=\left(\sum_{s\in C\land k>0}k\right)-\left(\sum_{s\in C\land k<0}\abs{k}\right)=Z_{f}-P_{f}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{f}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{f}$
\end_inset

 分别表示 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 所围区域（也用 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 表示）内零点（Zero）与极点（Pole）阶数之和。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Rouché]
\end_layout

\end_inset

如果 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $g(z)$
\end_inset

 在单连通区域 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

 内解析，并且在边界 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial D$
\end_inset

 上满足 
\begin_inset Formula $\abs{f(z)}>\abs{g(z)}$
\end_inset

，则 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)+g(z)$
\end_inset

 在 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

 内的零点个数相等。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
二者的零点个数分别为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\oint_{\partial D}\frac{f'(z)}{f(z)}\dd{z}=\ii 2\pi Z_{f},\quad\oint_{\partial D}\frac{f'(z)+g'(z)}{f(z)+g(z)}\dd{z}=\ii 2\pi Z_{f+g}
\]

\end_inset

考察第一个积分
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\oint_{\partial D}\frac{f'(z)}{f(z)}\dd{z}=\oint_{\partial D}\left[\ln f(z)\right]'\dd{z}=\eval{\ln f(z)}_{R\exp(\ii 0)}^{R\exp(\ii 2\pi)}=\ii\eval{\arg f(z)}_{R\exp(\ii 0)}^{R\exp(\ii 2\pi)}
\]

\end_inset

因此 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{f}$
\end_inset

 的几何意义为：沿 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial D$
\end_inset

 绕行一周，函数值 
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)$
\end_inset

 的辐角变化了 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{f}$
\end_inset

 个 
\begin_inset Formula $2\pi$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
类似地，考察第二个积分的被积函数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f+g=(1+\nicefrac{g}{f})f\implies\arg(f+g)=\arg(1+\nicefrac{g}{f})+\arg f
\]

\end_inset

由 
\begin_inset Formula $\abs{f(z)}>\abs{g(z)}$
\end_inset

 即 
\begin_inset Formula $\abs{g/f}\in[0,1)$
\end_inset

 可知 
\begin_inset Formula $\arg(1+\nicefrac{g}{f})\in(-\nicefrac{\pi}{2},\nicefrac{\pi}{2})$
\end_inset

，因此这一项对 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{f+g}$
\end_inset

 的贡献为零，从而有 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{f+g}=Z_{f}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

